## First Session

When starting your first Claude Code session:

1. Open project in terminal
2. Start Claude Code: `claude`
3. Claude will auto-load context from CLAUDE.md
4. Run `/arcflux:status` to see project state
5. Run `/arcflux:start <issue>` to begin work

## Troubleshooting

### ArcFlux not loading

```bash
# Check plugin installation
claude plugins list

# Reinstall if needed
claude plugins uninstall arcflux
claude plugins install arcflux
```

### GitHub CLI not authenticated

```bash
gh auth status
gh auth login
```

### Linear CLI not working

```bash
linearis auth
# Re-enter API key if needed
```

